text: Archischoenobius pallidalis is a moth in the family Crambidae. It was described by South in 1901.Archischoenobius pallidalis Insectoid.info. Retrieved 2017-05-30. It is found in China (Hubei, Fujian, Guangxi, Sichuan, Yunnan). ==References== Category:Moths described in 1901 Category:Schoenobiinae Category:Moths of China
